FBIS3-31199 "dreeu031__a94022" FBIS-EEU-94-031-A Document Type:Daily Report 15 February 1994 ANNEX Poland Chmielak Appointed To Head Finance Ministry LD1402214094 Warsaw PAP in English 2015 GMT 14 Feb 94 LD1402214094 Warsaw PAP Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Warsaw, Feb. 14--Prime Minister Waldemar Pawlak appointed Secretary of State and Deputy Finance Minister Henryk Chmielak as head of the Finance Ministry, the government press office reported on Monday. Henryk Chmielak has got a PhD in economics. In the years 1971-1987 he worked at the Higher School of Social Sciences and the Main School of Planning and Statistics (SGPIS.) From 1987 till 1991 he worked at the Central Office of Planning (CUP.)
